   Healthy Avocado Toast‚Ä¶ A Protein Packed Breakfast with Eggs and
   Avocado‚Ä¶!!! Simple, Nutritious, & Perfect for any meal of your day‚Ä¶ All
   in 10 minutes‚Ä¶

   Avocado Egg Toast - Pepper Delight #pepperdelightblog #recipe #avocado
   #avocadoeggtoast #healthy #eggtoast #breakfast #10minutesrecipe
   #avocadotoast #toastrecipes #toastwithsunnysideegg #eggrecipes
   #proteinbreakfast Rain, Rain, Rain‚Ä¶ it‚Äôs been raining crazy for the
   last two weeks and I just feel like crawling under my blanket, stay
   warm n cozy, and  sleep a lot more. Do you guys feel the same on rainy
   days? And when you wake up, you wish to have a hot piping cup of coffee
   and a warm breakfast, ready on the table‚Ä¶ I would love to have a toast
   with sides for breakfast!

   Avocado Egg Toast - Pepper Delight #pepperdelightblog #recipe #avocado
   #avocadoeggtoast #healthy #eggtoast #breakfast #10minutesrecipe
   #avocadotoast #toastrecipes #toastwithsunnysideegg #eggrecipes
   #proteinbreakfast My regular breakfast menu is mostly of Indian dishes;
   either some sort of a savory crepe, or steamed rice/wheat cakes.
   Although they are rich and healthy, they are not a good choice for a
   lazy morning. Smoothies and cereals are our go-to options for a quick
   breakfast, even eggs; my husband does eggs many ways and they turn out
   pretty good always. He loves eggs and has a couple of tricks up his
   sleeve to quickly cook eggs, be it poached, hard boiled, fried, or even
   microwaved!! So when it comes to any egg based recipes I am
   experimenting with, I leave the eggs with him; Of course I want them to
   look perfect in my recipe photos, and I know that he being a
   perfectionist does a wonderful job with the cooking and presentation!!

   Avocado Egg Toast - Pepper Delight #pepperdelightblog #recipe #avocado
   #avocadoeggtoast #healthy #eggtoast #breakfast #10minutesrecipe
   #avocadotoast #toastrecipes #toastwithsunnysideegg #eggrecipes
   #proteinbreakfast So this recipe is yummy and simple, there is hardly
   any recipe to speak about. All you need are:
     * Sliced bread ‚Äì toasted, any variety would work.
     * Eggs ‚Äì poached or fried, but keep the yolks runny.
     * Avocadoes ‚Äì sliced.
     * Seasoning ‚Äì salt and pepper.

   This warm n crunchy toast is a perfect dish for any meal of the day and
   you can try out wide varieties of it with different toppings of your
   choice.

   Avocado Egg Toast - Pepper Delight #pepperdelightblog #recipe #avocado
   #avocadoeggtoast #healthy #eggtoast #breakfast #10minutesrecipe
   #avocadotoast #toastrecipes #toastwithsunnysideegg #eggrecipes
   #proteinbreakfast Enjoy, Happy Cooking!!!

   Follow me on Instagram, try out the recipes and tag #pepperdelightblog
   and rate to all your pictures of Pepper Delight recipes you prepare.
   Avocado Egg Toast - Pepper Delight #pepperdelightblog #recipe #avocado
   #avocadoeggtoast #healthy #eggtoast #breakfast #10minutesrecipe
   #avocadotoast #toastrecipes #toastwithsunnysideegg #eggrecipes
   #proteinbreakfast
   Print
   Avocado Egg Toast
   Prep Time
   5 mins
   Cook Time
   5 mins
   Total Time
   10 mins

   Healthy Avocado Toast‚Ä¶ A Protein Packed Breakfast with Eggs and
   Avocado‚Ä¶!!! Simple, Nutritious, & Perfect for any meal of your day‚Ä¶ All
   in 10 minutes!
   Course: Breakfast
   Cuisine: American
   Keyword: avocado egg toast, egg toast
   Servings: 2
   Author: Akhila
   Ingredients
     * 2 slices of bread
     * 1 avocado (sliced lengthwise)
     * 2 eggs
     * Salt and pepper
     * Lime juice (to drizzle, optional)
     * Cilantro leaves (garnish, optional)

   Instructions
    1. Heat a little oil in a pan on a medium flame.
    2. Crack the eggs into the pan and cook sunny side up for 3 to 4
       minutes until the whites are set & yolks still runny.
    3. Toast the bread slices and arrange the avocado slices on top of it.
       Drizzle lemon juice over the avocados.
    4. Top the toasts with eggs.
    5. Season with salt and pepper. Garnish with chopped cilantro leaves.

